Installation
------------

For installation instructions, look at the file INSTALL.


Documentation
-------------

RELACS comes with an extensive html-based documentation.
See the INSTALL file for instructions how to generate
the documentation. You can read the documentation
with your favorite web browser / html viewer in
doc/html/index.html
You can also access the documentation from the Help->Help
menu or from the RELACS web page.

You also find lot's of information in the RELACS web pages. See
www.relacs.net


More information about RELACS
-----------------------------

The project home page is http://www.relacs.net.
RELACS is currently hosted by sourceforge (http://relacs.sourceforge.net).

You find a list of all people contributing to RELACS 
and their email adresses in the file THANKS.

The file AUTHORS lists the people that were and are contributing code to RELACS.

There is also a ChangeLog and a NEWS file.

